map_npcs.name: Boostgem Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Have you found any more crystals on your journey?
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
We've been researching these gems that occur naturally in the surrounding areas.
They seem to boost the strength of Oochamon, maybe give one of these a try?

map_npcs.name: Cave Guard
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Can't let you through without the boss's permission.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: This tunnel is off limits!

map_npcs.name: Engineer Al
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Any luck with the Lavaboard Prototype?
They took off through that there cave just to the East.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, you must be the new guy, yeah? 
Did the Professor Lyra send you my way?
Ya see, we have a bit of a problem. 
Someone's run off with our Lavaboard Prototype.
They took of sprinting through the cave to the East, if you can retrieve it that'd be a huge help!{objective:Retrieve the stolen Lavaboard Prototype}

map_npcs.name: Raider Zara
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Fine, fine, I'll go...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Oi, this is my stash! Get outta here!

map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Hmmm, I suppose you'll suffice.
I'm sure we'll be seeing eachother soon.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
My, my, you must be {player}.
I've heard of your work so far, but I'd like to propose a small test of your skills.

map_npcs.name: Crew Denny
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I think I'm gonna take some time to go cool off...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
You'd think working so close to lava flows would be way too hot...
And it is!

map_npcs.name: Crew Dustin
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Oh, my bad, there was a pebble in my boot!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Watch where you're goin I'm workin' here!

map_npcs.name: Researcher Charles
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Thanks, that helped a lot!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hmm, the oochamon in this area seem to be mostly Flame-type.
But I guess that makes sense considering where we are...
...
Oh, hey, I just caught these, help me test their performance!

map_npcs.name: Cave Guard
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Stay safe, we have a perfect safety record and I hope you'll maintain that.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, got the boss's permission?
Good, it's not safe on the other side of this cave.

map_npcs.name: Distracted Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Now, where did I leave that vial...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, was I in your way?
Sorry about that, I tend to get distracted from time to time.
How about a friendly battle to make up for it?
Just kidding! I don't have any Oochamon of my own.
Here, take these instead!

map_npcs.name: Busy Crew
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: It's looking pretty unstable.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Looks like it could be a while before this tunnel's safe to enter.

map_npcs.name: Crew Jim
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Fine, fine, I'll get back to work in another five minutes...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Me? I'm on my break.
And I'm definitely not slacking off.

map_npcs.name: Bored Crew
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: *Sigh...*
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
I'm so bored, there's nothing to do right now...
Here, take these, I don't have any use for them...

map_npcs.name: Engineer Al
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Great, you'll do just fine on our next request! Here's your completed Lavaboard!
Now, as for our next request...
There's a rather rare material further North of here.
If you hop on your Lavaboard and ride to the West, you'll get where you need to go.{objective:Ride the Lava River West}
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, perfect, you're back!
If you'll pass me the Lavaboard Prototype...
Hmm... I'll hand this off to another Engineer to tune it.
In the meantime, I'd like to test your strength!
Get ready for another battle!

map_npcs.name: Engineer Al
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
The settlement's a bit of a work in progress.
But we're still hard at work!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Having any luck out there? You can return here any time!

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Mr. Nice
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Ohoho? It appears you have bested me, friend. Please take this!
May we meet further down this road of destiny!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, hello there my good friend, it would seem you've rescued me from my vaguely cuboidal prison once again!
Without further ado, let us begin our promised battle!

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Shopkeep Cait
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: *Sigh* Back to work for me I guess...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Welcome to my store, would you like to buy anything?
Wait, I'm not on the clock right now...
Wanna battle?

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...

map_npcs.name: Sign
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
→ Old Training Facility
↓ Access Tunnel

map_npcs.name: Sign
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Beware of Lava! 
Cooling Balms Recommended

map_npcs.name: Suspicious Fellow
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: What happens in mystery building stays in mystery building.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: No, go away.

map_npcs.name: Suspicious Fellow
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Enter at your own peril, you won't be able to leave until you find the exit!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Psst, hey you, you seem pretty strong.
There's a cave below here that constantly shifts and changes if you're interested...
Enter at your own peril, you won't be able to leave until you find the exit!

map_npcs.name: Engineer Al
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Do be safe, the tunnel itself may be completed, but we still have to finish adding some supports!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Perfect timing! We've just recieved word that the Access Tunnel has been completed.
Could you deliver that Strange Flower Sample to Professor Lyra?
If you head South through this tunnel you'll reach her in no time! 
{objective:Travel South through the Access Tunnel, and deliver the Flower Sample to Professor Lyra.}
Ah, and don't think I've forgotten about your reward, here you are!

map_npcs.name: Crew Tyler
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Oh, if you intend to return to the Hub you can use the Access Tunnel.
It's directly south of the settlement here.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: The cave's off limits for a bit, we're doing work in here.

map_npcs.name: Explorer Dave
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Whew, it sure is hot around here, my map of the area nearly caught fire!
Watch your step around here, it's super not-safe!

map_npcs.name: Chest
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: You opened the chest...
